dot-to-dot-sweep (1.3) stable; urgency=low

  * Make leaderboard URLs configurable for future-proofing.
  * Game now starts in full screen mode by default.
  * Added keyboard and gamepad support.
  * Make obscured balls be slightly translucent to prevent cheap deaths.
  * Add high resolution graphics.
  * Fix bug in score particle generation which caused score effects to be
    incorrect sometimes.
  * Other graphical improvements.
  * Multi-architecture support for Android port.
  * Add Steam port, including achievements and display name integration.

 -- Todd Cope <todd@tcubedsoftware.com>  Tue, 23 May 2023 18:54:21 +0000

Dot to Dot Sweep (1.2.1) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix issues with Android port that were preventing it from working on many
    devices.

 -- Todd Cope <todd@tcubedsoftware.com>  Tue, 19 Feb 2019 22:57:43 +0000

