dot-to-dot-sweep (1.1.1) stable; urgency=low

  * Optimize score particle effects to eliminate in-game framerate stuttering.
  * Fix issue where the mouse cursor would not be displayed on the title screen
    if you exited the game state while it was hidden.

 -- Todd Cope <todd@tcubedsoftware.com>  Sun, 16 Apr 2017 15:19:25 +0000

dot-to-dot-sweep (1.1) stable; urgency=low

  * Implement desktop mode.
  * Rebalance scoring to ensure a better balance between cautious and aggressive
    play styles. Playing it safe and making it through more levels is now a
    viable way of competing for a high score.
  * Add visual aid to collectible dots to make the game more playable by people
    with color blindness.
  * Add setup wizard to simplify and clarify settings.
  * Run setup wizard the first time the game is opened.

 -- Todd Cope <todd@tcubedsoftware.com>  Wed, 03 Aug 2016 18:34:00 +0000

